item.title: Why Pumpkin Seeds Are a Smart Snack Choice
item.description: You can buy pumpkin seed oil in different forms from grocery and health food stores. Pumpkin seeds are a rich source of protein, unsaturated fatty acids, vitamins, and minerals that may reduce your risk of getting chronic diseases, such as cancer.
